<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
      i18n:domain="rosetta">

<head>
    <title metal:fill-slot="title">Rosetta</title>
    <!-- Plone style sheet -->
    <style type="text/css" media="screen">@import url(plone.css);</style>
    <!-- Launchpad style sheet -->
    <style type="text/css" media="screen">@import url(launchpad.css);</style>
</head>

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
    <div tal:replace="structure view/prefLangPortlet" />
    <div tal:replace="structure view/countryPortlet" />
    <div tal:replace="structure view/browserLangPortlet" />
</metal:rightportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

    <h1>Welcome to Rosetta!</h1>

    <p class="documentDescription">
        Rosetta is a tool for translating open source applications into
        your language. You can read more <a href="+about" title="About Rosetta">
        about Rosetta</a> or follow the links below to start translating.
    </p>

    <ul>

        <li tal:condition="not: request/lp:person">
            You might like to
            <a href="+login">log in</a>.
        </li>

    </ul>

    <h1>Translations in Ubuntu</h1>

    <p>Rosetta is the primary translation system for the Ubuntu Project. You
    can help translation any application in Ubuntu, or any of the Ubuntu
    derivative distributions, using this web interface. Select a release
    from the list below:</p>
    
    <div style="margin-left: 50px;">

        <p tal:repeat="distrorelease context/translatable_distroreleases">
            <img src="/++resource++product_icon.gif">
            <b>Version <span tal:replace="distrorelease/version" /> "<span
            tal:replace="distrorelease/title">distrorelease
            title</span>"</b>&nbsp;[&nbsp;<a tal:attributes="href
            string:/distros/${distrorelease/distribution/name}/${distrorelease/name}/+translations">Translate</a>&nbsp;]
            <br />
            <span tal:replace="distrorelease/summary">product
            summary</span>
        </p>

    </div> <!-- indent -->

    <h1>Translatable Applications</h1>

    <p>The following open source applications can currently be translated as
    part of the Rosetta Translation Project. Select an application to
    translate it into your own language, using only the your web browser. If
    your favourite open source application is not listed here, you can see
    if it is <a href="products">registered with the Launchpad</a> and then
    start to translate it immediately!</p>

    <div style="margin-left: 50px;">
    
        <p tal:repeat="product context/translatable_products">
            <img src="/++resource++product_icon.gif"> <b><span
            tal:replace="product/title">product title</span></b>
            [ <a tal:attributes="href
            string:/products/${product/name}/+translations">Translate</a> ]
            <br />
            <span tal:replace="product/summary">product
            summary</span>
        </p>

    </div> <!-- indent -->

    <p>Find or register <a href="products">another open source
    application</a> for translation.</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
